              li
                | Identification information generated by the use of cookie technology
              li
                | Location information
            p.num-wrapper-inside
              span.num-inside
                | ③
              span
                | To use for marketing and other information analysis
                br
                | (Type of User Information that will be handled)
            ul.inside
              li
                | Name
              li
                | Email address
              li
                | Date of birth
              li
                | Age
              li
